.SH NAME
tmp.3ot0T6rW6x \- Control and inspect Ableton Live via local Remote Script
.SH DESCRIPTION
ableton-cli is a non-interactive command line interface for operating Ableton Live
through a local Remote Script endpoint.
.IP
Usage: ableton\-cli [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
.IP
Control and inspect Ableton Live through a local Remote Script.
